# GrantCraft Backend API Test Requests
# Use with REST Client or similar tools

### Check if backend is running
GET https://grantcraft-backend-320165158819.us-central1.run.app/

### Health check (debug endpoint)
GET https://grantcraft-backend-320165158819.us-central1.run.app/api/debug/health

### Ping endpoint
GET https://grantcraft-backend-320165158819.us-central1.run.app/api/debug/ping

### Test login functionality
GET https://grantcraft-backend-320165158819.us-central1.run.app/api/debug/test/login
    ?username=test@example.com
    &password=password123

### Check for errors
GET https://grantcraft-backend-320165158819.us-central1.run.app/api/debug/errors
    ?password=GrantCraft2025!Debug

### Test database connection
GET https://grantcraft-backend-320165158819.us-central1.run.app/api/debug/test/database
    ?password=GrantCraft2025!Debug

### General API health
GET https://grantcraft-backend-320165158819.us-central1.run.app/api/health

### Check API docs
GET https://grantcraft-backend-320165158819.us-central1.run.app/api/docs